Third Department,

September, 1972

(September 5, 1972) The People of the State of New York ex rel. Frank A. Ciavarelli, Petitioner, v. Paul C. Agnew, as Director of Dannemora State Hospital, Respondent.

Application for writ of habeas corpus pursuant to CPLR .7002 (subd. [b], par. 2) denied. Greenblott, J. P., Cooke, Sweeney, Simons and Kane, JJ., concur.
